      "file_path": "policy-endpoints/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 248,
      "message": "My small suggestion: \"org.springframework.boot\" is a collections of \"org.springframework\" libraries. Maybe we could insert only the necessary \"org.springframework\" libraries rather than \"org.springframework.boot\" collections. (E.g. org.springframework:spring-core and org.springframework:spring-web)",
